<HEADLINE> Strawberry Joins Spring Program </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TAMPA, Fla. (AP) -- New York Yankees outfielder Darryl Strawberry  
started the next phase of his comeback from colon cancer surgery 
and lingering knee problems Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
